            "title": "港股開市︱初段飆升 恒指漲656點報25772點 滙控高開6.23%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美伊達成為期兩周的停火協議，外圍股市應聲抽升，港股今早在長周末假期過後復市亦顯著造好。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數開市報25772點，升656點或2.61%。恒生科技指數開報4817點，升137點或2.95%；國企指數以8598點開市，升141點或1.67%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普遍揚升，滙控(00005)開報138.1元，升6.23%；友邦(01299)開報90.45元，升4.99%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報121.9元，升2.87%；騰訊(00700)開報504.5元，升3.13%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國價油價急挫，兩大油股受壓。中海油(00883)開報25.6元，跌5.26%；中石油(00857)開報10.48元，跌2.69%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15845890-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e9%a3%86%e5%8d%87-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e6%bc%b2656%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125772%e9%bb%9e-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b6-23",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-08 09:33:25",
